Effect of #COVID #Vaccination in #BreastFeeding: JAMA
 
Study N=84 found robust secretion of #SARSCoV2 IgA & IgG #antibodies in breast milk for 6 wks after #COVID19 #Vaccine. This offers potential protective effect against
infection in baby.
